Do you understand what LD50 actually means? Don't get me wrong, I'm not trying to make you feel bad, I'm just trying to give you some kind of idea as to what it means.

LD50 is the dose of a substance that's lethal for 50% of the population. Therefore, LD50 does not vary  from person to person, and cannot. That said, I would also recommend some kind of Sv dosage, so that physicists can point and laugh people reading this can get some concept of the sheer amount of radiation coming off this thing.







